Class XFormParameters

java.lang.Object
  |

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class XFormParameters
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

A catch-all structure for transformation parameters. The transformation typically will be map-projections, datum transformations, and affine transformations.
